quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  43,16,"Kana kuti (Allah) vakatora vanasikana kubva mune zvavakasika, uye ivo (Allah) vakakusarudzirai imi vanakomana"
  43,17,"Uye kana umwe wavo akaudzwa nezvemashoko (ekuzvarwa kwemwanasikana) zvaanotaura kune Mupi wenyasha (Allah), chiso chake chinosviba uye anozadzwa nekutsamwa"
  43,18,"Uyo anokudzwa achishongedzwa (achipfekedzwa siriki negoridhe, mukadzi), uye asingakwanisi pakupokana kutaura mashoko ari pachena"
  43,19,"Uye vanoita ngirozi izvo dziri varanda veMupi ane nyasha (Allah), vakadzi. Vakamboona kusikwa kwazvo here? Uchapupu hwavo hwuchanyorwa uye vachabvunzwa"
  43,20,"Uye vanoti: “Dai kusiri kuda kweMupi ane nyasha (Allah), tingadai tisina kuzvinamata.” Havana ruzivo nazvo, uye hapana chavanoita kusara kwekunyepa"
  43,21,Kana kuti takavapa rimwe Bhuku mushure meiri (Qur’aan) iro ravarikubatisisa
  43,22,"Asi vanoti: “Takawana madzibaba edu vachitevera imwe nzira nechitendero, uye tinozvitungamirira kuburikidza netsoka dzavo.”"
  43,23,"Uye saizvozvo, hatina kutuma muyambiri mushure mako (Muhammad (SAW)) kune guta ripi zvarwo (vanhu), asi vaigara zvakanaka pakati pavo vakati: “Zvirokwazvo, takawana madzibaba edu vachitevera imwe nzira nechitendero, uye zvirokwazvo ticharamba tichitevera tsoka dzavo.”"
  43,24,"(Muyambiri) akati: “Kunyangwe ndakuunzirai gwara rakanaka pane ramakawana madzibaba enyu achitevera?” Vakati: “Zvirokwazvo, hatitendi mune zvawakatumwa nazvo.”"
  43,25,"Naizvozvo takavadzorera (takavaranga), uye tarisai ndeapi akazova magumo eavo vakaramba (Islaam)"